title: Pregame photos: Fans pose by Big Texas as Texas and Oklahoma prepare for Red River Showdown
text: Texas fans, from left, Trisha Rodriquez, Michelle Castillo, Tencha Rodriquez and Matthew Castillo take a selfie with Big Tex before the 2015 Red River Showdown NCAA football game against Oklahoma at the Cotton Bowl on Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Dallas. (Smiley N. Pool/The Dallas Morning News)
